*Dobrih* ljudi su uvek poželjni u društvu. (Good people are always welcome in the company.)

*Dobri* ljudi su uvek podržani. (Good people are always supported.)

Oni su naučili da cene *dobre* stvari. (They have learnt to appreciate good things.)

Oni traže *dobro* u svakom čoveku. (They look for the good in every person.)

Neki ljudi su veoma *dobri*. (Some people are very good.)